name: Agro Soar
overview: Oh no! Agro's big mouth has gotten him into trouble again. Even he should have known better than to insult a wizard, and now he's been transported into a pre-historic cartoon within his own TV! Can you help Agro soar past the dinosaurs and dangers that stand between him and the real world? It won't be easy, but if it was, Agro wouldn't need any help,right?
